{"tid":884102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【離奇】地圖上明明有卻看不見了！北海道小島突然「失蹤」","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:50:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa847ba1e3ac664950755a3eb10da6f2ca594d2","tid":884102,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"北海道北端本來有一個名為「鼻北」的小島被紀錄在地圖上，有座標亦有人曾經見過它，但最近有人前往堪察時卻發現小島不見了。<br />\n<br />\n鼻北小島在地圖上被標記在距離北海道猿払村約500米的外海上，曾調查日本各地島嶼47歲的清水浩史，為了出版《秘島圖鑑》下一集，今年9月前往視察鼻北小島，卻沒找到。<br />\n<br />\n在國際法當中，島嶼定義為即使潮漲也會露出水面的陸地區域，海上保安廳表示，島嶼測量工作是在1987年實施，記錄顯示該處有一座高於海平面約1.4米的島嶼；猿払村漁業公會內也有上了年紀的人士表示︰「在昭和50年代時期，那一帶曾有小島，當時(出海)都要繞路。」可是現在小島已不知所蹤。<br />\n<br />\n海上保安廳計劃著手調查，航海情報課課長輔佐藤井智雄表示：「有可能是風雪等因素，使得小島受侵蝕而消失。」<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181031&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58858327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181031%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58858327&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=fd802189\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181031%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58858327&h=6cbb1d3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181031&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58858327</a>"},{"pid":"539652c3dfaf5053ff284a31d3173ee3c81acb84","tid":884102,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"日本沉沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe76873cfafbd71fa1ed2a71e1de6cc3d1a3afa0","tid":884102,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"融撚晒d冰係咁上下"},{"pid":"86ae5383ff6f5488f6ae1246f358fe664d698cc4","tid":884102,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"baby不見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d98c40325f4944f3c4f2c78b9f123af360c20f9","tid":884102,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"填番上去(學黃岩礁) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c848ca1b4f4d7a25e92a962b24a1a906990dca","tid":884102,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:46:28.000Z","msg":"又地震又海嘯又融冰<br />\n唔沉先奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399264d80bdad8c433fb1cffc3840c70d3982324","tid":884102,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:50:27.000Z","msg":"北鼻不見了"}]}